Tucked away in the calm of Assagao, Jasmine Journeys @jasminejourneys.stay felt less like a stay and more like a home I didn’t know I needed. With slow mornings, cozy corners, and every detail so thoughtfully done, it’s the kind of place that doesn’t just welcome you—it holds you. Perfectly nestled between Goa’s buzzing hotspots like Anjuna and Vagator, and just a short drive from Mapusa, the closest city - it gave me the perfect mix of stillness and spontaneity.
